### Online Shopping API - Testing Endpoints

# Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7183
@contentType = application/json

##################################
### PRODUCTS ENDPOINTS
##################################

### Get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

###
### Get a specific product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

###
### Get products by category (Electronics)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/category/Electronics

###
### Get products by category (Accessories)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/category/Accessories

##################################
### CART ENDPOINTS
##################################

### Create a new cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/create
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###
### Get cart details (replace {cartId} with actual cart ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1

###
### Add product to cart (Product ID 1, Quantity 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1/add-item?productId=1&quantity=1

###
### Add another product to cart (Product ID 2, Quantity 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1/add-item?productId=2&quantity=2

###
### Add Laptop (high price product) to cart (Product ID 1, Quantity 1 more)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1/add-item?productId=1&quantity=1

###
### Update cart item quantity (Product ID 1, new quantity 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1/update-item?productId=1&quantity=3

###
### Get Purchase Summary (shows discount logic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1/summary

###
### Remove item from cart (Product ID 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1/remove-item?productId=2

###
### Get updated cart after removal
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1

###
### Clear entire cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1/clear

###
### Verify cart is empty
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/1

##################################
### DISCOUNT TESTING SCENARIOS
##################################

### Scenario 1: Create new cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/create
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###
### Scenario 1: Add Laptop (75000) - Subtotal 75000, should trigger 10% discount
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/2/add-item?productId=1&quantity=1

###
### Scenario 1: Check summary (should show discount)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/2/summary

###
### Scenario 2: Create another cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/create
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###
### Scenario 2: Add USB-C Cable (800) - Below 5000 threshold, no discount
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/3/add-item?productId=3&quantity=1

###
### Scenario 2: Check summary (no discount expected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/3/summary

###
### Scenario 2: Add Mechanical Keyboard (8500) - Total 9300, discount should apply
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/3/add-item?productId=4&quantity=1

###
### Scenario 2: Check summary again (discount should now apply)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/3/summary
